miot.typedef.device

类 Service

  • java.lang.Object
    • miot.typedef.device.Service

  • public class Service
extends java.lang.Object
    This class used to describe the Miot device ability. A Miot devcie can be composed of several services. A service usually include three type information: Action, Property and Event.
